by setting personal goals is one way to stay focused and happy.  =>

By setting goals, a person becomes focus and motivated to reach those goals.  Once you reach a goal that you set, this inner happiness takes over and you feel proud of yourself.  It motivates you to keep going and push yourself even further.
You can be the person to encourage others and keep them motivated.  But  => B
always remember to have your own goals that work for you that you focus on.
Just because your friend lost 20 pounds in 2 months does not mean you are a failure for only losing 10 pounds in the same amount of time.
